data.title: Album: Forgive Me By: Maher Zain
data.meta_description: Maher Zain - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains lyrics from several songs by Maher Zain. It includes the songs "Forgive Me", "My Little Girl", "Mawlaya", "Number One For Me", and "Paradise" among others. The songs focus on themes of love for God, asking for forgiveness, family bonds, and finding peace. They contain Arabic and English lyrics with melodies composed and arranged by Maher Zain.
